Clabir Corp and AmBrit Corpsaid they called off their plans for Clabir to buy the 16 pctvoting interest in AmBrit that it does not already own.    The companies said they agreed not to pursue the mergerbecause several actions recently taken by AmBrit would meansubstantial delays in completing the deal.    They said they might revive merger plans at a later date orseek other ways for Clabir to increase its holdings in AmBrit. Reuter&#3;